{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙携美蚕娘下山赶集，途中谈论婚姻往事。抵达市集后遭遇焦毒手下的地痞寻衅，项少龙以柴刀大展身手，将十余名地痞尽数击败，赢得围观群众喝彩。乌氏倮的管事陶方看中项少龙的武艺，以每月五十铜钱聘其为保镖，随马队前往邯郸。项少龙与美蚕娘依依惜别，留下二百铜钱供其生活，自己踏上寻秦始皇之路。本章展现了项少龙穿越后初显军事训练实力的场面，也刻画了他与美蚕娘的感情羁绊与无奈分离。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "你怎样会嫁给那两兄弟的？你自己的家人在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "奴家住在朝太阳要走三天的地方，有一天他们两兄弟带来一张虎皮、一张熊皮、十张貂皮、五条牛、一百头羊来向爹换我，这么丰厚的妆奁是我们族内从未曾听过的，于是我就嫁给了他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "那年你几岁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "十四岁！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "什么？那还未到合法的年龄呀！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "以前赶集最少要走十个时辰，自从有人建了这条运兵道后，四个时辰便可到达市集，省时多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这些武士是走镖的，专门负责替商贾运送财帛，是很赚钱的差事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "哈！终于有适合我的工作了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不！我再不能失去你这个丈夫。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看！左边那群汉子就是土霸焦毒的兄弟，他们正盯着我们，怎么办好呢？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他们定是晓得焦毒找我那件事，还以为我已成为焦毒的女人，所以见换了你出来，均惊异不定，今天可糟了，不如立即走吧！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "娘子不用慌，有为夫在此，谁也不能伤你半根毫毛。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她们是白夷人，最擅养马，男女都是很好的猎人，没有人敢欺负他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上马三十铜钱！上马三十铜钱！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "在这里杀人是否要坐牢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么是坐牢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "杀人有没有人管？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "除自己族人外，谁都不会理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不是要和这么多人打架吧？他们有剑啊！我们可以把换来的钱给他们。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_du_xia_shou",
      "speaker_name": "焦毒手下",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "美蚕娘！焦大哥在哪里？这臭汉是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jiao_du_xia_shou",
      "text": "你们的焦大哥给老子宰掉了，要报仇的赶快放马过来。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jiao_du_xia_shou",
      "text": "来吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "老天爷啊！你真是勇武！奴家以后都不怕恶人了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "知道怎样去邯郸吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有人听过这个地方，却不知怎样去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "壮士请留步！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "本人陶方，乃乌氏倮大爷手下十二仆头之一，壮士口音奇怪，不知是何方人士？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "我和内人是桑林村人，陶爷请我来，不知有什么关照？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "壮士有没有兴趣弄大笔的钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "愿陶爷有以教我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "以壮士惊人的身手，确可以一挡百，若你肯做我的保镖，我可以每月给你五十个铜钱，壮士意下如何？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那足够我们一年的生活。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "条件很吸引人，可是我们还要到邯郸去哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项壮士定是没听过我们乌大爷的威名，他就是邯郸首屈一指的'畜牧大王'，我们在各地收购足够马匹后，便会运往邯郸，壮士若做我的保镖，是一举两得的美事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "不过我要带她同行呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "放心吧！我们除收购健马外，还挑购各山地的美女，所以壮士携美同行，一点问题都没有。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我使人打扫地方给贤夫妇歇息，换过新衣，明天黎明动程回邯郸去。壮士惯用哪种武器，若是剑的话，我立即送你一把邯郸'陈老铁'打造的好剑，刚才你拾的那把可以扔掉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "到邯郸要走多久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "快马十日可达，但像我们那种走法，沿途又收购马匹、美女，最少要一个月的路程。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dou_liang",
      "speaker_name": "窦良",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄这么有本事，有机会倒要领教一下。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "不用怕窦良，迟早我会找个机会教训他一顿，什么恶人我项少龙也不害怕。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "城市的人都很奸诈，奴家怕不习惯那种生活。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "有我保护你，怕什么呢？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "桑林村住的都是好人，生活丰足，一年比一年好，现在焦毒那群恶棍全给打死了，更是太平乐土，夫君啊！不若我们回到那里居住，快快乐乐直至老死，奴家为你生儿育女，不是更好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "不如这样吧！我去向陶方借一百个铜钱，该足够你两年生活费，而我则到邯郸闯天下，一有成就便回来接你去，那不是两全其美吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "speaker_name": "美蚕娘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那岂不是要和你分开吗？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_mei_can_niang",
      "text": "快则几个月，迟则一、两年，我一定会回来的。别忘记我是老天爷派来的，所以绝不会死掉。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    }
  ],
